<h3>For Customers</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Browse and search local clothing shop products</li>
  <li>View product details, pricing, and shop information</li>
  <li>Contact shops directly via WhatsApp for purchases</li>
  <li>Post reviews and ratings for products after purchase</li>
  <li>Earn and redeem cashback through the wallet feature</li>
  <li>Location-based shop and product discovery</li>
</ul>

<h3>For Shop Owners</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Create and manage a digital storefront</li>
  <li>List products with images, descriptions, and pricing</li>
  <li>Receive customer inquiries via WhatsApp</li>
  <li>Access customer search analytics and demand insights</li>
  <li>Manage cashback offers for customers</li>
  <li>Subscription-based access to features</li>
</ul>

<p>
